{"word":"G1825 - ἐξεγείρω - exegeírō - ex-eg-i'-ro - Raise up","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐξεγείρω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">exegeírō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ex-eg-i'-ro</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Raise up</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - எழுப்பு, நிலைநிறுத்து"},{"paragraph":"to rouse up, stir up, incite"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1537 - ἐκ - ek - ek/1537\">G1537</a> and <a href=\"#/G1453 - ἐγείρω - egeírō - eg-i'-ro/1453\">G1453</a>; to <i>rouse fully</i>, that is, (figuratively) to <i>resuscitate</i> (from death), <i>release</i> (from infliction): - raise up.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1127/1127\">G1127</a>, <a href=\"#/G1453/1453\">G1453</a>, <a href=\"#/G1454/1454\">G1454</a>, <a href=\"#/G1825/1825\">G1825</a>"}]}